trans-unit.source: The items passed in to this parameter may have optional metadata attached to them called `LogicalName`, `Target`, and `Access`.
trans-unit.target: Elementer som er sendt til denne parameteren kan ha valgfrie metadata som er tilknyttet kalles `LogicalName`, `Target`, og `Access`.

trans-unit.source: The `LogicalName` metadata is used to specify the internal identifier for the resource.
trans-unit.target: Den `LogicalName` metadata brukes til å angi den interne identifikatoren for ressursen.

trans-unit.source: The `Target` metadata can specify the path and filename to which the task copies the file, after which it compiles this new file into the assembly.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the version information for this assembly.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir versjonsinformasjon for denne samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The format of the string is *major.minor.build.revision*.
trans-unit.target: Formatet for strengen er *major.minor.build.revision*.

trans-unit.source: The default value is 0.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er 0.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the documentation for the `/v[ersion]` option in [Al.exe (Assembly Linker)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon, kan du se dokumentasjonen for den `/v[ersion]` alternativet i [Al.exe (Assembly Linker)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The version information for this assembly.
trans-unit.target: Versjonsinformasjon for denne samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the .ico file to insert in the assembly.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir filen *.ico å sette inn i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The .ico file gives the output file the desired appearance in Windows Explorer.
trans-unit.target: Filen *.ico gir utdatafilen ønsket utseendet i Windows Utforsker.

trans-unit.source: This property corresponds to the `/win32icon` option in [Al.exe (Assembly Linker)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen samsvarer med den `/win32icon` alternativet i [Al.exe (Assembly Linker)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The .ico file to insert in the assembly.
trans-unit.target: Filen *.ico å sette inn i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a Win32 resource (.res file) to insert in the output file.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en Win32-ressurs (.res-fil) til å sette inn i utdatafilen.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the documentation for the `/win32res` option in [Al.exe (Assembly Linker)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon, kan du se dokumentasjonen for den `/win32res` alternativet i [Al.exe (Assembly Linker)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The Win32 resource (.res file) to insert in the output file.
trans-unit.target: Win32 ressursen (.res-fil) til å sette inn i utdatafilen.
